_sText:
Ok, this is my first map I've ever published, but I hear that I'm pretty talented. It's a defusal map with 2 bomb sites (A and B) and I must say that it's great! Lots of different ways to play.

It took me about 5 days to make, and I made it from scratch, and I'm not 100% happy about it, more like 99% but there's always something you want to make better so I think it's as good as it gets.

Visually it's stunning, the gameplay rules. I've mixed funny parts from other maps including de_dust2, de_aztec and de_cbble (Only thing from cbble is all boxes in bomb site B)

If you're running a server and wish to run my map please contact me first. (I've got tons of more fun maps) 

E-mail: johan16_g@hotmail.com
